<SectionCard cardID="requests" cardTitle="Make A Request" cardSize="half">
  <div class="card_text">
    <p>
      If it's WPRBXmas, you can use the form below to send Jon a listener
      request.
    </p>
    <p>
      Once your request has been submitted, you'll receive a confirmation e-mail
      and your request will be automatically added to the listener request
      queue.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you accidentally send Jon incorrect data, please don't submit another
      request!
    </p>

    <p>
      Instead, use the link provided in your confirmation email to edit your
      request. Your corrections will be automatically merged into the listener
      request queue.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you have trouble accessing/using the site's request form, you can
      submit your request directly through Google <a
        href="https://forms.gle/BZXu559k8u2fjQiL8"
        target="_blank">here</a
      >.
    </p>
  </div>
  <details id="requests__details">
    <summary id="requests__summary"
      >Click here to open the Listener Request Form!</summary
    >
    <iframe
      id="requests__form"
      src="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfgK_jfRP_N-nXJYicxhuHh5aRtNSvOxOVGC2sGzsV0WQzrcw/viewform?embedded=true"
